text: Soumaila Diabate (born 22 November 2004) is a Malian footballer. He plays as midfielder for the Austrian Bundesliga club FC Blau-Weiß Linz on loan from FC Liefering. ==Career == Diabaté started his career at Guidars FC. In January 2023 he went to Austria to join FC Red Bull Salzburg. FC Red Bull Salzburg Homepage In Salzburg he was loaned to FC Liefering in the Second league. In April 2023 he made his debut for Liefering . He came in for Tolgahan Sahin during the half-time break on the 21st matchday of the 2022/23 season against Kapfenberg SV. In September 2024, Diabaté was loaned to Bundesliga club FC Blau-Weiß Linz.
